DUPLICATES CHECK¶

It is possible that some offers are removed and published again with exact the same information under another identification number. In this stage, they are filtered and removed from the dataset.

In [20]:
# Using geolocation, retrieve the region of the offer using the geocordinates if avaliable

geolocator = Nominatim(user_agent="http")

for i in df_1[(df_1['Bundesland'].isnull()) & (df_1['Latitude'].isnull() == False ) & (df_1['Longitude'].isnull() == False)].index:
    x = df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Latitude'].item()
    y = df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Longitude'].item()
    location = geolocator.reverse("{}, {}".format(x, y))
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bundesland'] = location.raw.get('address').get('state') 
    
# Retrieve the region of the offer using the postal codes if avaliable
    
nomi = pgeocode.Nominatim('de')

for i in df_1[(df_1['Bundesland'].isnull()) & (df_1['Latitude'].isnull() ) & (df_1['Longitude'].isnull()) & (df_1['Postleitzahl'].isnull() == False)].index:
    x = str(df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Postleitzahl'].item()).replace('.0','')
    location = nomi.query_postal_code(x)[3] 
    #print(location)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bundesland'] = location

In [23]:
# Using geolocation, retrieve the region of the offer using the geocordinates if avaliable for the
# suspected item with an error 

for i in df_1[(df_1['Bundesland']!="Berlin") & (df_1['Bundesland']!="Brandenburg") & (df_1['Bundesland']!="Hessen")
             & (df_1['Latitude'].isnull() == False) & (df_1['Longitude'].isnull()== False) ].index:
    x = df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Latitude'].item()
    y = df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Longitude'].item()
    location = geolocator.reverse("{}, {}".format(x, y))
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bundesland'] = location.raw.get('address').get('state') 

# Using geolocation, retrieve the region of the offer using the postalcode if avaliable for the
# suspected item with an error 

nomi = pgeocode.Nominatim('de')
for i  in df_1[(df_1['Bundesland']!="Berlin") & (df_1['Bundesland']!="Brandenburg") & (df_1['Bundesland']!="Hessen")
             & (df_1['Latitude'].isnull()) & (df_1['Longitude'].isnull()) & (df_1['Postleitzahl'].isnull() == False) ].index:
    x = str(df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Postleitzahl'].item()).replace('.0','')
    location = nomi.query_postal_code(x)[3] 
    #print(location)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bundesland'] = location

print(location.raw)

FLATS IN BERLIN¶

# Filter out the offers from Berlin 

df_1 = df_1[df_1.Bundesland == 'Berlin'].copy()

df_1 = df_1 [(df_1.OnlineId != '26GMH5E') & (df_1.OnlineId != '27TTQ56')]

    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('000','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace(' 00','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('xx','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('HH','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace(r'\b(\d{1})\b.OG','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('re','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('li','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('.Apt','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('XX','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace(',Hinterhau','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('. chts','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('(DG)','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace('/ fi ab 01.08.22','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Strasse'].str.replace(' 0','',regex=True)

# Complete missing information for the offers with avaliable rent price and utility costs

for i in df_1[(df_1['Warmmiete'].isnull()) & (df_1['Nebenkosten'].isnull() == False) & (df_1['Kaufpreis'].isnull() == False)].index:
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Warmmiete'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Kaufpreis'] + df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Nebenkosten']
In [84]:
# Complete missing information for the offers with avaliable rent price and rent prince plus utility costs

for i in df_1[(df_1['Nebenkosten'].isnull() == True) & (df_1['Warmmiete'].isnull()==False) & (df_1['Kaufpreis'].isnull()==False)].index:
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Nebenkosten'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Warmmiete'] - df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Kaufpreis']

In [116]:
# As in Immonet, some observations indicates that the heating costs are included in the total rent costs.
# There is no way to tell the difference between utility costs and heating costs.
# Hence, this observations are dropped

df_1 = df_1[(df_1.Heizungskosten != 'in Warmmiete enthalten') & (df_1.Heizungskosten != 'in Nebenkosten enthalten')]
In [117]:
# Some prices are given after request. Hence, this indication should be defined as a nan value.
# The rest can ben turn into float 

for i,j in zip(df_1['Heizungskosten'].index,df_1['Heizungskosten']) :
    try:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Heizungskosten'] = float(j)
    except:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Heizungskosten'] = np.nan

# Remove unnecesarry strings

for i,j in zip(df_1[df_1['Kaution'].isnull() == False]['Kaution'],df_1[df_1['Kaution'].isnull() == False].index):
    
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution'].astype(str) 
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution'].str.replace('&a;#8364;','', regex=True)
                
   
    if  '.' and ',' in df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].item():
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('.','', regex=True)
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace(',','.', regex=True)
        
        
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('als Mietbrgschaft','',regex=True)      
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('Kaution oder Brgschaft','',regex=True)    
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('.-','',regex=True)     
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('--','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('-','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('Euro','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('EUR','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace(',00','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('(Bankbrgschaft)','',regex=True)
    df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =   df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].str.replace('( 3 x Grundmieten v . 488,00 )','',regex=True)

   # Transform string values into numeric values 
    
    if i == '2':
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaufpreis']*2
        break
        
    
    try:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] =  float(df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].item())
        if df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'].item()<20:
            #print('Ja')
            df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1']*1000
            #print(df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'])
                
    except:
        
        if i == ' nach Vereinbarung' or i == 'nach Vereinbarung' or i=='Nach Vereinbarung':
            df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = np.nan
            
        for k in mn3:
            if k in i:
                df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaufpreis']*3
                break
                
        for k in mn2:
            if k in i:
                df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaufpreis']*2
                break
        
        for k in gn:
            if k in i:
                df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution'].str.replace(k,'')
                break
        
        if '2,5 Monatsmieten' or '25 Kaltmieten' in i:
            df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaufpreis']*2.5
           
        if '1 Kaltmiete' in i:
            df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaufpreis']
            
        if i == ' 1.200 + Eintrittsgeld 75':
             df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = 1275
                
        if i == '900,00  Geschftsanteile + 75,00  Eintrittsgelt':
            df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = 975
            
                
        if i == 'keine':
             df_1.loc[df_1.index == j,'Kaution_1'] = 0


df_1.loc[df_1.Kaution=='462,00 Kaution, 100,00 Eintritt, 160,00 Anteile','Kaution_1']= 462+100+160

In [145]:
# Correct labelling <- This variable is used for the merging of the datasets of both real state portals

for i in df_1['Kategorie'].index:
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Kategorie'].item() == 'Terassenwohnung':
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Kategorie'] = 'Terrassenwohnung'
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Kategorie'].item() == 'Loft':
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==i,'Kategorie'] = 'Loft-Studio-Atelier'

        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Zimmer'] = float(j)
    else:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Zimmer'] = np.nan

# Extract in a different column the plausibel dates.
# Just the registers with a unique date are extracted

for i in df_1[(df_1['Baujahr'].isnull() == False)].index:
    try:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Baujahr_1'] = int(df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Baujahr'])
        if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Baujahr_1'].item()<1700:
             df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Baujahr_1'] = np.nan           
    except:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Baujahr_1'] = np.nan

# Normalize the string attributes of the variable

for i in df_1[(df_1['Bezug'].isnull() == False)].index:
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in n_v :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'nach Vereinbarung'
        
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in ab_sofort :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'sofort'
        
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in fertig :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'nach Fertigstellung'
    
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in kurzfristig :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'kurzfristig' 
    
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in ver :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'vermietet'        

    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in verkauf :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'nach Verkauf'

            
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() == 'Haus in Planung':
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'in Planung'
            
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in zahlung :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'nach Kaufpreiszahlung'
            
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in beur :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'nach Beurkundung'
      
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in mittel :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = 'mittelfristig'
    
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item() in nan :
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = np.nan

In [170]:
# Extract the avaliability dates

datet = list()

for i in df_1[(df_1['Bezug'].isnull() == False)].index:
    
    y= re.search(r"^\b(\d{2})\b.\b(\d{2})\b.\b(\d{4})\b$", df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item())
    if y!= None:
        x = df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item()
        x = x.replace('.','/')
        x = x.replace('-','/')
        #x = pd.to_datetime(x)
        print(x)
        x = pd.to_datetime(x,format = '%d/%m/%Y')
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = x
        datet.append(i)

In [172]:
# Extract just the year for Q3, Saison, etc from whole string in the case it finishes with the year.

for i in df_1[(df_1['Bezug'].isnull() == False)].drop(datet).index:
    w = re.search(r"\b(\d{4})\b$", df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug'].item())
    if w != None:
        if int(w.group(0))>2010:
            df_1.loc[df_1.index == i, 'Bezug_1'] = w.group(0)
            datet.append(i)
            
# Check the unique years

    else:

        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'vermietet'] = 1

In [182]:
# Adjust and reduce the attributes of the variable

for i,j in zip(df_1[df_1['Zustand'].isnull()== False]['Zustand'],df_1[df_1['Zustand'].isnull()== False].index) :
    if 'Altbau (bis 1945)' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'Altbau'
        continue
    if 'gehoben'in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'gehoben'
        continue
    if 'gepflegt'in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'gepflegt'
        continue
    if 'Neubau' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'Neubau'
        continue
    if 'renoviert' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'renoviert'
        continue
    if 'saniert' or 'teilsaniert' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'saniert'
        continue
    if 'sanierungsbedrftig'in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'sanierungsbedrftig'
        continue
    if 'renovierungsbedrftigt'in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'renovierungsbedrftigt' 
        continue
    if 'Abrissobjekt'in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'Abrissobjekt'
        continue
    if 'baufllig' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'baufllig'
        continue
    if 'entkernt' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'entkernt'
        continue
    if 'Rohbau' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'Rohbau'
        continue
     
    # Attribute brought from another variable. This is also present in Immonet
    
for i,j in zip(df_1[df_1['Ausstattung'].isnull()== False]['Ausstattung'],df_1[df_1['Ausstattung'].isnull()== False].index) :
    if 'neuwertig'in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Zustand'] = 'Neuwertig'

# Extract the unique current use of the flat

for i,j in zip(df_1[df_1['Geschosse'].isnull()== False]['Geschosse'],df_1[df_1['Geschosse'].isnull()== False].index) :
       
    x = re.search(r"^\b(\d{1})\b",i )
    y = re.search(r"^\b(\d{2})\b",i )
    if(x!=None):
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse_1'] = int(x.group(1))
        if 'Untergeschoss' in df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse'].item():
            df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse_1'] = -1*df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse_1'].item()
        else:
            pass
    if(y!=None):
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse_1'] = int(y.group(1))
        if 'Untergeschoss' in df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse'].item():
             df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse_1'] = -1*df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse_1'].item()
        else:
            pass
    if df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse'].item()=='Erdgeschoss':
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Geschosse_1'] = 0

# Create dummy variables representing each attribute and assign the values according to the flat

for i,j in zip(df_1[df_1['Aussenbereich'].isnull()== False]['Aussenbereich'],df_1[df_1['Aussenbereich'].isnull()== False].index):
    if 'Wintergarten' in i or 'Garten' in i or 'Gartenmitbenutzung'in i or 'Gartenanteil' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Garten'] = 1
    else:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Garten'] = 0
    if 'Dachterrasse'in i or 'Terrasse'in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Terrasse'] = 1
    else:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Terrasse'] = 0
    if 'Loggia'in i or 'Balkon' in i:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Balkon'] = 1
    else:
        df_1.loc[df_1.index == j, 'Balkon'] = 0

# Extract the number of avalaible parking lots

for i,j in zip(df_1[df_1['Parkmoeglichkeit'].isnull()== False]['Parkmoeglichkeit'],df_1[df_1['Parkmoeglichkeit'].isnull()== False].index) :
       
    x = re.search(r"\b(\d{1})\b",i )
    y = re.search(r"\b(\d{2})\b",i )
    z = re.search(r"\b(\d{3})\b",i)
    if(x!=None):
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Anzahl Pltze'] = int(x.group(1))
    if(y!=None):
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Anzahl Pltze'] = int(y.group(1))
    if(z!=None):
        df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Anzahl Pltze'] = int(z.group(1))
    if  'Stellplatz' in i:
         df_1.loc[df_1.index==j,'Anzahl Pltze'] = 1
